feature: Located in Annapolis Maryland
description: VIN  Winecafe is built on family history and passion for food wine and beer The name VIN meaning wine in French also defines the vintage feel of our housesetting in the eclectic Eastport neighborhood of Annapolis Our restaurant is approachable local and reminds us of comfortable inviting experiences and places that we have loved Relax by the fire during winter with a glass of wine enjoy one of our craft beers or share a handformed brick oven fired pizza on the patio in spring Our food is American with many ingredients sourced from local organic providers Our influences and roots include Mediterranean Californian and New England cuisines combined to create the fresh American cuisine unique to VIN  We aspire to the European ideal of smaller more frequent meals both simple and delicious at VIN  meals are meant to be shared Please join us and experience the feel and tastes of VIN
